result.title: White Zombie
result.overview: A young man turns to a witch doctor to lure the woman he loves away from her fiancé, but instead turns her into a zombie slave.

result.title: King of the Zombies
result.overview: On a spooky island, three stranded travelers find an evil doctor working with foreign spies and in control of zombies.

result.title: The Living Ghost
result.overview: A retired detective, Nick Trayne, is hired to look for a missing banker. During the investigation, the aforementioned banker returns in a zombie-like state. Trayne must track down the madman responsible for the banker's state.

result.title: I Eat Your Skin
result.overview: A playboy adventure novelist joins his publisher on an expedition to Voodoo Island in the Caribbean, where a cancer researcher is being forced to turn the tribes-people into zombies.

result.title: Shock Waves
result.overview: In the dark days of World War II, the Nazi High Command ordered its scientists to create a top secret race of indestructible zombie storm troopers - un-living, unfeeling, unstoppable monstrosities that killed with their bare hands. They were known as The Death Corps. No member of this horrific SS unit was ever captured by the Allies - and, somewhere off the coast of Florida, they have survived...

result.title: Night of the Zombies
result.overview: After an experiment gone wrong, a virus that turns people into zombies spreads throughout New Guinea, whilst a female reporter, her cameraman and a team of four commandos sent to investigate try to survive the attack.

result.title: The Children
result.overview: A nuclear-plant leak turns a bus-load of children into murderous atomic zombies with black fingernails.

result.title: Lifeforce
result.overview: Space vampires spread disease and destruction throughout London after an exploratory mission to Halley's Comet brings them back to Earth.

result.title: The Boneyard
result.overview: Children turned into zombies wreak havoc in a coroner's building with just a burned-out psychic, an experienced cop and two coroners to stop the madness.

result.title: Pot Zombies
result.overview: Radioactive weed turns people into zombies with the munchies for human flesh!

result.title: Days of Darkness
result.overview: Humanity makes its last stand as zombies emerge to take over the world in this cinematic tale of gore and chaos.

result.title: Dance of the Dead
result.overview: On the night of the high school prom, a town gets overrun by zombies and it is up to all the geeks who didn't get dates to the dance to save their community.

result.title: Virus Undead
result.overview: An infection transmitted by diseased birds is causing corpses to reanimate in search of human flesh. As the army of the undead grows, a medical student and his friends find themselves surrounded by zombies, with nowhere to run.

result.title: Zombie Farm
result.overview: A voodoo priestess raises a zombie horde to exact her personal revenge.

result.title: Super 8
result.overview: J.J. Abrams and Steven Spielberg join forces in this extraordinary story of six friends who witness a train wreck while making a super 8 movie, only to learn that something unimaginable escaped during the crash.

result.title: DeadHeads
result.overview: Deadheads is a "zombedy" that is sure to impress--pleasing both horror and action-adventure fans alike. Yup, you heard it first. Horror, meets comedy, meets action adventure!  DEADHEADS is a return to the great comedy/adventure films of the 80's like "Back to the Future" and the "Goonies".

result.title: Zombie Warz: Falls the Shadow
result.overview: Three years after the War, the United States is destroyed. Civilization has devolved into anarchy and tribalism.

result.title: A Little Bit Zombie
result.overview: Infected by a virus during his bachelor party, Steve attempts to resist a deadly transformation from man to monster. But his strange mannerisms and overwhelming desire for brains are the least of his worries. With an obsessed Zombie Hunter hot on his trail, Steve must learn to resist his greatest temptations all while keeping it together so as not to incur the wrath of his Bridezilla-to-be.

result.title: In the Flesh
result.overview: A war breaks out as humans battle to rid the planet of brain eating Zombies. After the living win, scientists subdue the Zombies and release these Partially Deceased Syndrome (PDS) sufferers back into the community.

result.title: Zombie Massacre
result.overview: A team of soldiers who are assembled to help end a zombie outbreak in a Romanian town.

result.title: April Apocalypse
result.overview: After years of yearning for the girl next door, Artie finally builds the courage to woo her... only to find out the girl of his dreams and best friend, April, is moving away - sending Artie into a deep depression. Three years later, the lion inside tells Artie to "go find April and make her yours".  Artie crashes his car on the way... and wakes up a week later in the middle of a zombie outbreak.

result.title: Code Red
result.overview: A top-secret nerve gas created by Stalin during WW2 goes missing for over 70 years and is discovered in modern day Bulgaria.

result.title: The Zombie King
result.overview: A man makes a pact with him to destroy the underworld and bring chaos to earth.

result.title: Dug Up
result.overview: Chaos takes over a rural town after a trio of residents accidentally conjure a zombie outbreak. But the townspeople have enough firepower to blow the walking dead back to hell!

result.title: Dead Snow 2: Red vs. Dead
result.overview: The lone survivor of Dead Snow's Zombie attack wakes in the hospital with his severed arm replaced with the arm of his Nazi nemesis, sparking a rampage of revenge by raising an undead army of his own.
